  "detailed_description": "A small horror about a young man Stefan, whose life turns into a nightmare. Help him cope with the situation and understand what happened.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou are expected by:<br />\r\n- 10 levels<br />\r\n- enemies who are not averse to feasting on you<br />\r\n- riddles to be solved<br />\r\n- items that are just waiting to be found<br />\r\n- 2 endings<br />\r\n- about 1 hour of gameplay<br />\r\n- constant desire to wake up.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHelp Stefan get out of his nightmare, one way or another.",
